# Summary
This documentation page describes the SendGrid destination integration for Amplitude, which enables sending user cohorts to SendGrid for email marketing campaigns and tracking email engagement metrics. The integration requires proper API key permissions, unique email addresses in cohorts, and mandatory field mappings for email, first name, and last name.

